Here is how to take your website live from the Cloudways you can check this for creating A records:
https://support.cloudways.com/how-do-i-take-my-website-live-from-cloudways/#tab-2

You can check your DNS propagation here:
https://www.whatsmydns.net


Please be informed that this issue is out of the support scope that we provide as we are not managing your domains. 
They are being managed by the domain provider.
If you want us to manage your DNS we provide an add on DNS made easy you can subscribe to that
We provide a DNS Management service (as an Add-on) if you want us to manage DNS for you. 
Here's how you can activate it: https://support.cloudways.com/how-to-activate-dns-madeeasy-addon/

